武汉医生患病后自己诊治、隔离：我们的麻醉师插管没有护目镜，就用泳镜。
Wuhan doctor himself after the illness, diagnosis, isolation: our anesthesiologist intubation does not have goggles, use swimming glasses.
李想俣。
Minamata Lee.
